<svg width="100%" viewBox="0 0 680 750" role="img" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="">
  <title style="fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);stroke:none;color:rgb(255, 255, 255);stroke-width:1px;stroke-linecap:butt;stroke-linejoin:miter;opacity:1;font-family:&quot;Anthropic Sans&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:400;text-anchor:start;dominant-baseline:auto">Zero Trust Access Control Diagram</title>
  <desc style="fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);stroke:none;color:rgb(255, 255, 255);stroke-width:1px;stroke-linecap:butt;stroke-linejoin:miter;opacity:1;font-family:&quot;Anthropic Sans&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:400;text-anchor:start;dominant-baseline:auto">Access control flow showing subject identification, authentication, device posture, policy decision point, and access grant or deny outcomes for a Zero Trust web application.</desc>
